1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:04,500
[Never Too Late]

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:06,600
Ping'an.

3
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,000
We've gotten to know each other recently.
[Episode 5]

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,700
There are some things I want to tell you.

5
00:00:13,700 --> 00:00:18,100
So, starting from today, can we officially start dating?

6
00:00:18,900 --> 00:00:21,500
No, I don't mean that.

7
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:23,600
Xiao Ke, it's useless to wear headphones now.

8
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:26,200
Let's go, I will take you for tea.

9
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:28,800
- I'll also have tea?
- Let's go.

10
00:00:32,900 --> 00:00:35,100
Do you want me to teach you a method to friendzone someone?

11
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:36,900
You hurry out first.

12
00:00:36,900 --> 00:00:38,600
Okay.

13
00:00:39,400 --> 00:00:41,100
Bye.

14
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,900
As long as she's not in a relationship with Zhang Ping'an,

15
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,500
we can be lovers.
[Wedding Date]

16
00:01:08,900 --> 00:01:13,500
Most of my relatives from my hometown are no longer there.

17
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:16,300
The people who can come on the wedding day won't be many.

18
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:18,000
What about your family?

19
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:22,500
In my family, there are only Xile's second aunt-in-law and fourth aunt-in-law.

20
00:01:22,500 --> 00:01:25,900
As for the rest of the relatives, I can't be bothered to invite them.

21
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:29,000
Okay, as you say.

22
00:01:30,700 --> 00:01:33,900
In case Xile and Zhang also get married,

23
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:36,200
they will definitely gossip about me behind my back.

24
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,400
Xile and Zhang are getting married?

25
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:41,400
Last time they came home, weren't they not yet in a relationship?

26
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,800
Xiao Zhang just called me.

27
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:47,200
He said he wanted to formally confess to Xile today.

28
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:50,600
If it's fast, they can also get married by the end of the year.

29
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:52,000
It…

30
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:58,300
It's good news. I…

31
00:01:58,300 --> 00:02:00,800
Ding Ran, is a wolf is chasing you?

32
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:03,100
You're flustered all day.

33
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:07,900
Sorry, the number you dialed cannot be reached for now.

34
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:12,200
Ding Ran, I have a shirt to give you. It has our names on it.

35
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:14,500
I specially embroidered them on.

36
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:21,800
Ding Ran, I want to date you.

37
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,800
What do you think?

38
00:02:25,210 --> 00:02:29,700
♫ When it's late at night, I feel powerless ♫

39
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:33,800
Jiang Xile, I've planned our next ten years.

40
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,000
Do you want to open it and take a look?

41
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:39,700
♫ Insomnia all night yesterday and today  ♫

42
00:02:39,700 --> 00:02:43,100
♫ The blurry darkness from day to night ♫

43
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:46,700
Lu Liuliu, it's me, Ding Ran. Where is Jiang Xile now?

44
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:56,600
♫ The rain, like my tears, quietly seeps into my soul ♫

45
00:02:56,600 --> 00:03:01,800
♫ Just noticed I haven't looked at the world closely in a while ♫

46
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:04,600
Don't accept him. Don't like him.

47
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:08,700
♫ The most perfect summer and autumn are already yesterday ♫

48
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:12,500
♫ That figure has disappeared from the window ♫

49
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:16,100
♫ Only a few vague images remain ♫

50
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:19,400
♫ I wish I could return to that year ♫

51
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:24,100
♫ In the blink of an eye, several years have passed since summer and autumn ♫

52
00:03:24,100 --> 00:03:27,900
♫ We can't go back to the past ♫

53
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:32,000
♫ I regret not living in the moment ♫

54
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:37,800
♫ Your tears and my indifference ♫

55
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:41,400
Why is it that I plan and plan again and again

56
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:44,900
and the final result is always like this?

57
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,400
Ding Ran,

58
00:04:10,100 --> 00:04:11,800
morning.

59
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:20,000
I'm almost late for work. Can you give me a ride?

60
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:23,800
I'm in a hurry today. You take a taxi yourself.

61
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:27,300
Ding Ran.

62
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:35,300
Are you in such a hurry?

63
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,800
Let's go.
[Closed]

64
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,700
They've already closed.

65
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:42,100
No problem, come in.

66
00:04:42,100 --> 00:04:45,400
Junior President Qi, you're here. Everything is…

67
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:49,000
Junior President Qi?

68
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:52,600
This cafe is yours?

69
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:57,200
Sort of. Not really.

70
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,200
Come sit here.

71
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,900
I'll get something ready.

72
00:05:09,700 --> 00:05:11,300
What's going on?

73
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:13,900
You can end work early, I'll prepare it.

74
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:45,100
Try the coffee.

75
00:05:46,700 --> 00:05:48,400
You can make coffee?

76
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:50,600
That's impressive.

77
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:54,800
Can I fall sleep after drinking this?

78
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:57,600
It smells very delicious.

79
00:05:58,500 --> 00:06:01,000
And this cake, I made it myself. Try it.

80
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,500
Okay.

81
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,300
Is it delicious?

82
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:08,900
Yes.

83
00:06:08,900 --> 00:06:10,700
If it's delicious, have more.

84
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:12,300
Okay.

85
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,400
This is…

86
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:24,200
Surprised or not?

87
00:06:25,100 --> 00:06:27,000
Surprised.

88
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:38,700
Liuliu, let's get married.

89
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:40,900
Get married?

90
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:43,500
Qi Fei,

91
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:47,100
don't you think we've skipped too many steps?

92
00:06:47,100 --> 00:06:48,900
Steps.

93
00:06:50,300 --> 00:06:52,000
I see.

94
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:58,500
Will you marry me?

95
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:02,800
I wasn't talking about that kind of step. Please get up and sit properly.

96
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:10,800
Qi Fei, I won't marry you.

97
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:20,000
I know. You won't marry me.

98
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:25,200
Every time I try to establish a dating relationship with you, you always avoid me.

99
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:33,200
I don't know other than doing this, what else I can do.

100
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:36,700
I know this may be a bit too quick.

101
00:07:36,700 --> 00:07:40,300
So can we start by dating?

102
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:44,700
Qi Fei, it's not that I don't want to date you.

103
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:47,000
I'm not dating anyone.

104
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:49,000
You're a very good boy.

105
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:52,500
In the future, don't do this kind of thing again.

106
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:55,400
I have other things to do. I'm leaving.

107
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:58,400
Liuliu.

108
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,400
Ding Ran.

109
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,300
I need to talk to you.

110
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:20,100
I'm a bit tired today. Let's talk another day.

111
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:22,600
I… I'll be quick.

112
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:33,400
Ding Ran.

113
00:08:39,660 --> 00:08:41,348
Ding Ran.

114
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:46,200
Your dad and my mom happen to be away. I want to ask you

115
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:50,600
about my wound. The scar seems a bit deep.

116
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:53,300
Is there any way…

117
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:55,700
Why is there no water at home?

118
00:08:55,700 --> 00:08:57,800
It doesn't matter. It's a water outage.

119
00:08:57,800 --> 00:09:00,000
I'll go check.

120
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:05,800
There… There's water here.

121
00:09:05,800 --> 00:09:07,400
Is there?

122
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:12,800
I'll have Ding Ran ask the property management. Ding Ran, Ding Ran!

123
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:16,000
- Don't call him. I'll go myself.
- I'll go with you.

124
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:19,000
This kid isn't home. He left so many lights on.

125
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:22,400
They're gone.

126
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:30,800
You can use some scar removal cream on your wound.

127
00:09:32,100 --> 00:09:33,670
Okay.

128
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:36,000
I have another thing.

129
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:39,400
It's about my female colleague. She found out I had this surgery.

130
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:42,400
When she heard that I had a younger brother working in the breast surgery department,

131
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:47,400
- she wanted to ask--
- Jiang Xile, I'm not your younger brother.

132
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,400
What's wrong with you?

133
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:53,300
A few days ago, you helped me out. You seemed to care about me.

134
00:09:53,300 --> 00:09:55,100
Just now, you…

135
00:09:58,500 --> 00:10:02,500
Well, when we were at the hospital, you took good care of me.

136
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:05,400
But now you seem to be avoiding me. I'm all confused by you.

137
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,800
What exactly is our relationship?

138
00:10:08,700 --> 00:10:10,839
We're doctor-patient.

139
00:10:13,039 --> 00:10:17,360
I take good care of every patient, including you.

140
00:10:19,079 --> 00:10:22,579
All right, I see.

141
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:27,320
From childhood till now, it's always been just my wishful thinking.

142
00:10:30,740 --> 00:10:33,079
What do you mean by wishful thinking?

143
00:10:36,420 --> 00:10:39,580
Now that we all graduated, if I could date Ding Ran…

144
00:10:39,580 --> 00:10:41,820
If you could date Ding Ran, then what?

145
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:43,540
If I could date Ding Ran,

146
00:10:43,540 --> 00:10:47,540
I could take away something you like and piss you off.

147
00:10:47,540 --> 00:10:50,600
♫ Let's not forgive each other ♫

148
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,540
- Who asked you to target me!
- You.

149
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:53,600
What you?

150
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:56,899
When my confession is successful, I'll notify you first.

151
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:04,240
- On graduation day, it was clearly you and Xu Shanshan—
- I hope you won't bring up the events of graduation day again.

152
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:09,884
♫ The cost of time cannot be measured ♫

153
00:11:09,884 --> 00:11:13,632
♫ So don't worry too much about it ♫

154
00:11:13,632 --> 00:11:19,620
♫ Just like this, don't look back  ♫

155
00:11:19,620 --> 00:11:21,360
Ding Ran.

156
00:11:22,879 --> 00:11:24,359
What's up?

157
00:11:24,359 --> 00:11:26,620
I…

158
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:29,839
I want to date you. What do you think?

159
00:11:32,873 --> 00:11:36,020
♫ You wholeheartly go forward ♫

160
00:11:36,020 --> 00:11:39,119
Date her! Date her!

161
00:11:42,239 --> 00:11:44,000
Jiang Xile,

162
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,360
♫ I never expected to be forgiven ♫

163
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:49,660
I don't have time to participate in your boring life.

164
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:55,324
♫ A better life is something everyone should strive for ♫

165
00:11:55,324 --> 00:12:00,837
♫ Don't linger, just keep moving forward ♫

166
00:12:00,837 --> 00:12:03,620
♫ To have loved is enough ♫

167
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:06,500
The thing I regret the most

168
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:10,139
is confessing to you in public.

169
00:12:17,498 --> 00:12:26,433
♫ The cost of time cannot be measured ♫

170
00:12:26,433 --> 00:12:28,860
♫ So don't worry too much about it ♫

171
00:12:28,860 --> 00:12:31,699
What's so great about him? If I take the initiative to talk to you again,

172
00:12:31,699 --> 00:12:34,220
I'll write my name backward.

173
00:12:36,460 --> 00:12:38,200
Who do you think you are?

174
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:43,720
♫ I never expected to be forgiven ♫

175
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:45,960
♫ Doing things the wrong way can be very hurtful ♫

176
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:49,240
Lu Liuliu, I don't care what you're doing right now.

177
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:52,700
You listen to me first. I'll bet with you.

178
00:12:52,700 --> 00:12:57,399
If I like Ding Ran again, I will give you 8,888 yuan.

179
00:13:00,079 --> 00:13:03,660
How can there be such an annoying person in this world?

180
00:13:06,222 --> 00:13:11,811
♫ A better life is something everyone should strive for ♫

181
00:13:11,811 --> 00:13:17,818
♫ Don't linger, just keep moving forward ♫

182
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:33,220
Xile, have an egg.

183
00:13:33,220 --> 00:13:35,079
Uncle Ding, I've had enough. Don't bother.

184
00:13:35,079 --> 00:13:38,320
You haven't come for breakfast for several days. Did you quarrel with Ding Ran again?

185
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,780
How could it be?

186
00:13:39,780 --> 00:13:42,260
If he bullies you again, tell me. I will discipline him.

187
00:13:42,260 --> 00:13:43,899
No need, Uncle Ding.

188
00:13:43,899 --> 00:13:46,959
A son is meant to be disciplined.

189
00:13:46,959 --> 00:13:50,899
All right, you eat first. Your mom's stomach hasn't been well these days. I'll cook some porridge for her.

190
00:13:50,899 --> 00:13:52,460
Okay.

191
00:13:53,760 --> 00:13:56,160
Uncle Ding, thank you.

192
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:58,419
My mom is a bit difficult to take care of.

193
00:13:58,419 --> 00:14:02,960
She even said she wanted to exercise with you. But she couldn't persist for more than two days.

194
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,620
Silly kid, what are you talking about?

195
00:14:05,620 --> 00:14:07,500
We're family. No need to thank me.

196
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:09,680
Besides, your mom isn't hard to take care of.

197
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:14,339
The most difficult to care for in this family is that brat.

198
00:14:23,700 --> 00:14:25,219
Hasn't he gotten up yet?

199
00:14:25,219 --> 00:14:28,079
He left early in the morning.

200
00:14:29,959 --> 00:14:32,239
He went to work?

201
00:14:32,239 --> 00:14:35,259
He said there was some kind of exchange activity.

202
00:14:35,259 --> 00:14:37,580
I don't understand. He didn't say when I asked.

203
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:40,800
This kid has always been like this. He holds everything in his heart.

204
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:43,039
He doesn't discuss anything with others.

205
00:14:43,039 --> 00:14:44,476
Oh, yes.

206
00:14:45,620 --> 00:14:47,679
Wait a moment.

207
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,140
What's up?

208
00:14:53,919 --> 00:14:55,800
This is something Ding Ran asked me to give to you.

209
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:57,700
He said you left it on the sofa yesterday and he picked it up.

210
00:14:57,700 --> 00:15:00,340
- I left it?
- Go ahead and eat.

211
00:15:19,590 --> 00:15:21,360
[Scar Removal Cream]

212
00:15:24,119 --> 00:15:27,239
You can use some scar removal cream on your wound.

213
00:15:27,239 --> 00:15:29,700
What does he mean?

214
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:32,139
Sometimes cold, sometimes caring.

215
00:15:32,139 --> 00:15:34,919
[If the scar is obvious, you can use scar removal cream.]

216
00:15:34,919 --> 00:15:37,099
Crazy.

217
00:15:39,279 --> 00:15:42,380
Uncle Ding, I'm going to help wake my mom.

218
00:15:42,380 --> 00:15:46,720
From today on, we will change her unhealthy lifestyle together.

219
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,920
No need, let her sleep more.

220
00:15:50,460 --> 00:15:52,380
This kid.

221
00:15:53,420 --> 00:15:55,179
I see.

222
00:15:55,179 --> 00:15:59,379
Xiao Zhang, when you have time, come home for dinner.

223
00:15:59,979 --> 00:16:01,480
Recently, you and Xile—

224
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:03,920
- Mom.
- I'll talk to you when I have time.

225
00:16:03,920 --> 00:16:08,839
- Who are you calling?
I... I was calling Xiao Zhang.

226
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:13,460
You two haven't settled your relationship for so long.

227
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:15,219
I want to help you.

228
00:16:15,219 --> 00:16:18,279
Mom, don't call him again.

229
00:16:18,279 --> 00:16:21,480
It's awkward. I've already clearly rejected him.

230
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:23,959
We won't be in a relationship.

231
00:16:25,039 --> 00:16:26,759
Is that so?

232
00:16:26,759 --> 00:16:30,300
Mom. Why are you so calm?

233
00:16:30,300 --> 00:16:34,479
Don't you want to ask me why or tell me how good he is or anything like that?

234
00:16:34,479 --> 00:16:38,119
If I say that, will you continue to develop a relationship with him?

235
00:16:38,119 --> 00:16:39,019
No.

236
00:16:39,019 --> 00:16:41,400
Then that's it.

237
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:44,960
You must have tried dating him

238
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:49,200
and then realized you didn't like him. So you rejected him explicitly.

239
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:52,680
So, what should I say? Does it make any sense?

240
00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:55,440
Mom, you're so understanding.

241
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:57,519
Of course.

242
00:16:57,519 --> 00:17:01,600
Although I also hope you can get married,

243
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:06,459
life is so short. Of course, you should be with the person you like.

244
00:17:06,459 --> 00:17:09,720
Mom, you're so considerate.

245
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:12,100
But... to speak of it,

246
00:17:12,100 --> 00:17:14,819
do you have a crush?

247
00:17:14,819 --> 00:17:16,579
No.

248
00:17:17,360 --> 00:17:19,360
Impossible.

249
00:17:19,360 --> 00:17:22,060
I'm your mother, I understand these things.

250
00:17:22,060 --> 00:17:26,119
Looking at how you can't settle now, you must have a crush.

251
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:27,300
Tell me quickly.

252
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:29,360
Who is it exactly?
[Turtle Zhang]

253
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:31,659
Mom, I'm answering a call.

254
00:17:33,352 --> 00:17:35,059
Director Zhang.

255
00:17:35,059 --> 00:17:39,280
Jiang Xile! What's going on with you? You either take leave or play hookie.

256
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:41,412
Do you still want to work or not?

257
00:17:41,412 --> 00:17:45,239
- I'm taking a call, Mom.
- Wait a moment, Xile. When did you take leave?

258
00:17:46,680 --> 00:17:48,280
Director Zhang,

259
00:17:49,380 --> 00:17:51,660
the last time I took leave, I had a surgery.

260
00:17:51,660 --> 00:17:54,159
Today, I'm going to the hospital.

261
00:17:56,139 --> 00:17:59,880
- Baby. Baby, any problems with your work?
-Jiang Xile, you had surgery? What surgery did you have?

262
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:02,480
There's no one in the company who's more lively than you.

263
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:04,580
I haven't seen you missing any limbs.

264
00:18:04,580 --> 00:18:06,179
Don't make up an excuse.

265
00:18:06,179 --> 00:18:07,680
I didn't make up any excuse.

266
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:10,440
