267
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:12,560
I don't care if you're sick or attending a funeral.

268
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:15,380
Within ten minutes, I want to see you appear in the company.

269
00:18:15,380 --> 00:18:18,500
If you're really sick, come here even if you have to crawl.

270
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:24,340
Zhang Siqiang, stop talking. I'm resigning now.

271
00:18:24,340 --> 00:18:26,159
Jiang Xile, what do you mean?

272
00:18:26,159 --> 00:18:29,259
I quit, that's what I mean. Do you understand?

273
00:18:29,259 --> 00:18:30,800
If you don't, I'll say it again.

274
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:33,660
Do you understand lingerie? Do you understand design? Do you understand women?

275
00:18:33,660 --> 00:18:36,640
The whole company has been messed up by you all, such a motley crew.

276
00:18:36,640 --> 00:18:39,659
What a mess! Enough, goodbye.

277
00:18:39,659 --> 00:18:42,419
No, I mean, never see you again.

278
00:18:47,239 --> 00:18:50,499
Baby, you…

279
00:18:51,600 --> 00:18:54,420
You finally resigned.

